        <item>
            <title>1.11.0</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 10:28:36 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>35</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.11.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features

- **Opus 4.7 with 1M context** — new "Opus (1M)" choice in the launcher's model picker, alongside the existing "Sonnet (1M)".
- **X-High effort level** — new effort tier between High and Max (Opus 4.7 only), available in the launcher's effort picker.
- **Cleaner model name in the status bar** — IDs like \`claude-opus-4-7[1m]\` now render as "Opus 4.7 (1M)" in the status bar pill.

### Bug Fixes

- **Quitting after "Stop Session and Close" no longer warns about active sessions.** Choosing "Stop Session and Close" in the window-close dialog now terminates the underlying Node.js process synchronously, so Cmd+Q afterwards goes through cleanly instead of prompting "N session(s) still running".
]]></description>
