        <item>
            <title>1.10.1</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 14:21:37 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>34</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.10.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed plan mode hang after approving ExitPlanMode — the session would get stuck indefinitely when the user approved the plan; the root cause was `createWebviewPanel()` replacing the active message routing target, breaking control message flow back to the CLI

### Improvements
- Made EventEmitter error handling more resilient — a single listener error no longer prevents other listeners from firing
]]></description>
