        <item>
            <title>1.10.0</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 10:44:54 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>33</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.10.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- **Window close dialog** — Closing a window with an active session now shows a dialog with three options: Hide Window, Stop Session and Close, or Cancel
- **Hidden Windows menu** — Hidden windows now appear in the Window menu, making it easy to bring them back

### Changes
- Filtered out auto-generated observer sessions from the session list
]]></description>
